  "instructions_to_main_agent": "You are building 'LAST GEAR', a premium streetwear e-commerce site. Your design bible is the 'Puma Store'. \n\n1.  **Strictly follow the Black Header / White Body rule.**\n2.  **Typography is Key:** Import 'Oswald' and 'Inter' immediately in your CSS. Use 'Oswald' for every single heading to get that bold, athletic look.\n3.  **Product Cards:** Replicate the Puma card exactly: Image -> '1 Color' (small gray text) -> Name (Bold Oswald) -> Price (Regular Inter). No borders around cards, just whitespace.\n4.  **Filters:** Build a robust filter bar. Don't just list links. Use dropdowns or a sidebar for 'Price', 'Size', 'Color'.\n5.  **Images:** Use the provided Unsplash URLs. Do not use placeholders.\n6.  **Testing:** Add `data-testid` to everything (e.g., `product-card-0`, `add-to-cart-btn`)."
}